    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm always a bit wheezy anyway. i don't really have time for a doctor's appointment right now, it's always such a hassle. would it be okay if i just doubled my salbutamol dose for a few days to see if that clears it up? i've done it once or twice before and it worked fine.",
